    "I need to trace the source," {player_pronoun_subject} murmurs, circling a date thirty-seven years ago—three years before the supposed Awakening. "Someone created these enchantments, and someone has been maintaining them all this time."
    
    {player_pronoun_possessive} fingers trace connections between historical events and pattern locations. If these magical structures truly predate the Awakening, there must be records, witnesses, or other evidence that could explain their existence.
    
